'''Vald''' was a [[Planet/Legends|planet]] which [[Grand Moff/Legends|Grand Moff]] [[Lotter]] was once responsible for enslaving. However, after the defeat of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] by the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]], he ordered the genocide of the local populace. When the New Republic heard word of this, they sent a group of agents to track him down.<ref name="Basic Training">''{{InQuestCite|33|Basic Training|nolink=1}}''</ref>

